HEADWORD: Cross-spall
<hw>Cross"-spall`</hw>
<pr>(-sp?l`)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Spale</er> &
<er>Spall</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Shipbuilding)</fld> <def>One of the
